| Principle | Application |
|----------|-------------|
|  Plain Language | Avoid jargon. E.g., â€œAccess controls so no one sees what they shouldnâ€™t.â€ |
|  Clean Visuals | Use color-coded risk tables or diagrams to illustrate impact |
